*Dependeces - (Php, Apache) or XAMP;

*Api_Url : "https://olinda.bcb.gov.br/olinda/servico/PTAX/versao/v1/odata/CotacaoDolarPeriodo(dataInicial=@dataInicial,dataFinalCotacao=@dataFinalCotacao)?@dataInicial=\''.$diainicial.'\'&@dataFinalCotacao=\''.$diaAtual.'\'&$top=1&$orderby=dataHoraCotacao%20desc&$format=json&$select=cotacaoCompra,dataHoraCotacao"

*Objective - "Consume a real-time quote API from the Central Bank of Brazil."